\id 2TH - Abureni 
\h 2 Ate̠salonia̠ 
\toc1 Wa̠leghemeni I̠wal A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m A̠nwunom Ate̠salonia̠̠ Bho̠ 
\toc2 2 Ate̠salonia̠ 
\toc3 2 Ate̠s 
\mt2 Wa̠leghemeni I̠wal A̠d̠ire Wa̠ Apo̠l Age̠ Agi̠o̠m 
\mt1 A̠nwunom Ate̠salonia̠̠ 
\mt2 Bho̠ 
\imt1 Otighom 
\ip A̠d̠izo a̠nwunom d̠a̠ aso̠si̠ bho̠ na̠ e̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an na̠ egboloma̠ ma̠ omula̠ oru ta̠ Akrai̠st. D̠a̠ ebula̠ eb̠um egbika̠ a̠ponoma̠, awa i̠ru̠ru̠an ma̠a̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ i̠se̠n i̠se̠n, sa̠ awa i̠gba ma̠ o̠pu̠r a̠duom ta̠ Apo̠l i̠pi̠e̠ ma̠a̠, wa̠leghemeni i̠wal eruoma̠ ta̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ aro̠ ma̠ obhel ola̠ o̠ni̠ ologhom d̠o̠. D̠a̠ asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an onon, a̠d̠izo awa i̠ro̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a erugh ado̠l i̠te̠i̠, na̠ eb̠ologiom ma̠a̠ awa na̠ eb̠a̠ra̠ ma̠ omula̠ oru ta̠ Akrai̠st. 
\ip Onon a̠duom a̠nimeta̠n o̠gi̠o̠m i̠pu̠r a̠nwunom Ate̠saloni̠ka. Apo̠l age̠ ma̠ a̠duom onon ma̠ omutiom amu̠gho̠nyan d̠a̠ asu̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ wa̠leghemeni i̠wal omula̠ oru ta̠ Akrai̠st bho̠. D̠a̠ a̠duom onon, Apo̠l a̠leriom a̠d̠izo i̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ ed̠ia̠ emite kisa̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, sa̠ na̠ a̠leriom ma̠a̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, ma̠a̠ i̠karabh na̠ ado̠l i̠basi̠ ta̠ eb̠uiy emuzo d̠a̠ obhel irileghom ta̠ odi o̠ni̠ ola̠ ko orue d̠o̠ o̠mu̠gho̠nyan ola̠ ubhelegi ma̠a̠ “O̠karabh O̠ni̠ bho̠” (2:3), wa̠ ta̠ amara adamaghan Akrai̠st bho̠. 
\ip O̠ni̠ ogir ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠ amar agba a̠mutiom ezin wa̠ a̠bhon ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠mu̠gho̠n i̠na bho̠ ma̠ o̠ro̠ ti̠to̠i̠ny d̠a̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi d̠awa d̠a̠ obhel ali̠gam a̠ruzu na̠ egbika̠. Awa egir ekponom a̠ruzu d̠awa ma̠ agu̠o̠ Apo̠l na̠ ogbogir d̠o̠yo̠ igir bho̠, na̠ ebhiroma̠ od̠ighi ib̠eb̠i. 
\iot Aru̠mu̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ u̠ge̠ bho̠ 
\io1 Ogba o̠kparame̠ni̠ omula̠ oru ta̠ Akrai̠st \ior (1:1-12)\ior* 
\io1 I̠di̠ar ya̠ ta̠ emite kisa̠ Akrai̠st ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru \ior (2:1-12)\ior* 
\io1 Ipa̠n a̠kikiom na̠ o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ ima̠ra̠ ologi \ior (2:13—3:5) \ior* 
\io1 A̠ma̠rugh a̠nwunom ya̠ na̠ ema̠ra̠ ma̠ Akrai̠st na̠ ibheleguma̠ ekunuguma̠ \ior (3:6-18) \ior* 
\c 1  
\s1 Ibheleguma̠ 
\p  
\v 1 Ami̠ Apo̠l, na̠ Asai̠las, na̠ A̠timoti, na̠ o̠ge̠ na̠ oruom inyin ogbo ya̠ na̠ e̠gi̠ ma̠ aso̠si̠ d̠a̠ Ate̠salonia̠ bho̠, ya̠ i̠ro̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠ na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st ma̠a̠:  
\v 2 E̠no̠gho̠man na̠ ekima̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ bho̠, na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st e̠ro̠ na̠ inyin. 
\s1 Ali̠se̠bh 
\p  
\v 3 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, akpe̠ i̠yar o̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ eb̠la̠ kigiel ebula̠ agu̠o̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin na̠ a̠bhobh bho̠, sa̠ etula̠n wa̠ od̠i d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io d̠inyin na̠ abu̠gh e̠mi̠ bho̠.  
\v 4 Obha̠ bha̠ ezin wa̠ i̠yar na̠ obhin inyin na̠ obo d̠a̠ raso̠si̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ bho̠. I̠yar na̠ obo d̠a̠ a̠ma̠ne d̠inyin, na̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin, na̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ osibhom a̠ruzu d̠a̠ esa̠d̠io i̠damaghan na̠ egbika̠ ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ inyin bho̠. 
\s1 O̠kpo̠me̠ni̠ ologi d̠a̠ obhel ad̠agi̠an 
\p  
\v 5 I̠nye̠n na̠ eleriom ma̠a̠, A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠sobh ase̠ igielake̠, sa̠ na̠ e̠gba na̠ emutiom ma̠a̠ inyin o̠kpe̠ ma̠ od̠igh d̠a̠ irileghom d̠o̠yo̠, ma̠ agu̠o̠ inyin na̠ one ma̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 6 Agu̠o̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aro̠ ma̠ ola̠ igielake̠ bho̠, i̠na ta̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu ma̠ ogbo ya̠ na̠ enigha̠ inyin ali̠gam a̠ruzu bho̠,  
\v 7 sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠tenemeni inyin d̠a̠ ali̠gam a̠ruzu ya̠ na̠ e̠te̠i̠ inyin bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ ab̠aram na̠ i̠yar a̠tenemeni. I̠na ta̠ a̠gir o̠ku̠a ma̠ igiel Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s ta̠ ad̠u̠a d̠a̠ ote̠nai̠ny a̠mite a̠ru na̠ imoma̠na̠n itileduom ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠,  
\v 8 na̠ e̠ba anya ola̠ na̠ a̠mumor belembelem na̠ a̠rubhula̠, ma̠ obhin o̠kpe̠ ogbo ya̠ ologhom d̠o̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ i̠b̠agh e̠mu̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ Ib̠eb̠i O̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ d̠i̠yar A̠zizo̠s bho̠.  
\v 9 Ta̠ ogbikimeni awa ma̠ egbika̠ kid̠ud̠ul, sa̠ ta̠ o̠bagi̠o̠n awa o̠si̠ghe̠ d̠a̠ a̠misigh ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠limon isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠.  
\v 10 Igiel i̠na ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru, eb̠la̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ima̠ra̠ i̠na bho̠ ta̠ e̠bu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ i̠na, sa̠ ta̠ a̠d̠igh awa ma̠ ilologia̠n. Inyin od̠i ani̠ d̠a̠ o̠lo̠gh d̠awa, ezin bho̠ inyin oma̠ra̠ ma̠ i̠di̠ar ya̠ i̠yar u̠gba unigha̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 11 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a sa̠ i̠yar na̠ osiseiny na̠ onigha̠ inyin kigiel kigiel, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ alo̠gh agu̠o̠ a̠nigha̠ inyin ma̠ o̠ro̠ agu̠o̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ ta̠ erugh ado̠l wa̠ akpe̠ ma̠ agu̠o̠ ogbo ya̠ i̠na na̠ aso̠n bho̠ ma̠ orugh. I̠na a̠bhin a̠limon d̠o̠yo̠ a̠muzoghod̠iom eb̠la̠ ib̠eb̠i i̠walama d̠inyin, na̠ rogir ya̠ ologi ima̠ra̠ d̠inyin na̠ enuom inyin ogir bho̠.  
\v 12 I̠yar na̠ osiseiny o̠ku̠a b̠o̠ka̠ otutumeni ma̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s ma̠ ebula̠ inyin, sa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠tutumeni inyin nyen, d̠a̠ e̠ne̠ghe̠ ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ d̠i̠yar na̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st. 
\c 2  
\s1 O̠karabh O̠ni̠ Bho̠ 
\p  
\v 1 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠le̠gh inyin, ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ omula̠ oru ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s, na̠ a̠kokod̠ia̠n wa̠ i̠yar ta̠ ka̠ o̠te̠i̠ i̠na bho̠, ma̠a̠:  
\v 2 o̠ni̠ ko o̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠an d̠a̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an, o̠ni̠ ko okpa̠ra̠noma̠ nyen egboloma̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ ta̠ ekue e̠gba ma̠a̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ iwowa̠ d̠i̠yar, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠fugh o̠nu̠, bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ a̠lebh eru, sa̠ ta̠ e̠gba ma̠a̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠ru.  
\v 3 Agu̠o̠ ka̠ agu̠o̠ ta̠ e̠bhi̠bhi̠ri̠gi̠, o̠ni̠ ko oma̠ra̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ ma̠ ogelemeni inyin. Ezin bho̠, kisa̠ A̠d̠a̠ma̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠ru, a̠nwunom ta̠ ewia̠n a̠limon ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ sa̠ ta̠ e̠damaghan i̠na ma̠ o̠kparakpar agu̠o̠, sa̠ O̠karabh O̠ni̠ wa̠ ta̠ orobh o̠lo̠gh d̠a̠ e̠ba anya od̠im o̠to̠ bho̠ ta̠ a̠mutiom ozu.  
\v 4 O̠karabh O̠ni̠ bho̠ ta̠ adamaghan kabar kabar ola̠ a̠gboloma̠ ma̠ A̠zib̠a̠, sa̠ ta̠ abu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ ozu d̠o̠yo̠ a̠peleni kabar kabar ola̠ na̠ obhelegi ma̠ a̠zib̠a̠, bo̠d̠o̠ ola̠ na̠ o̠ko̠l. I̠na ta̠ agi̠ ka̠ aro̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de d̠a̠ Otu ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ nyen are̠ma ma̠a̠ i̠na A̠zib̠a̠.  
\v 5 Ka̠ inyin ta̠ orue o̠ru̠ru̠an, ami̠ agba gha̠n i̠di̠ar i̠nye̠n a̠nigha̠ inyin igiel bho̠ ami̠ i̠ro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 6 Ya̠a̠, i̠se̠n inyin na̠ ologhom abar wa̠ na̠ a̠sibh O̠karabh O̠ni̠ bho̠ na̠ a̠guri tu̠tu̠n ta̠ ate̠i̠ a̠ga̠i obhel wa̠ i̠na ta̠ a̠ru bho̠.  
\v 7 I̠se̠n bha̠ a̠limon e̠wo̠gi̠na wa̠ na̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ a̠nwunom o̠we̠le̠ osibh oloko bho̠ na̠ ake̠ ma̠ ogir. Ya̠a̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠sibh a̠limon bho̠ na̠ a̠guri bho̠ ta̠ a̠sibh tu̠tu̠n i̠na ta̠ a̠toka̠n.  
\v 8 I̠se̠ kisa̠ o̠ni̠ wa̠ osibh d̠o̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ ta̠ a̠mutiom ozu. Ya̠a̠, igiel Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s ta̠ a̠mula̠ a̠ru sa̠ ta̠ a̠pughe ma̠ obhubhulom d̠a̠ o̠nu̠ d̠o̠yo̠ a̠gigh O̠ni̠ wa̠ osibh d̠o̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠bhin isosorogia̠n d̠o̠yo̠ a̠kunugi i̠na.  
\v 9 Eruoma̠ O̠ni̠ wa̠ osibh d̠o̠ ma̠ oloko bho̠ ta̠ agi̠ na̠ od̠ighi i̠di̠ar ta̠ Eru bho̠, sa̠ ta̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien kere kere a̠limon a̠mutioghom relegh, a̠gir ilologia̠n igunugha̠,  
\v 10 sa̠ ta̠ a̠bhin a̠d̠ien kerekere i̠karabh ikoiny a̠gelemeni ma̠ ogbo ya̠ ta̠ ebhe bho̠. Awa ta̠ emugughu ekun, ezin bho̠ awa ima̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ otula̠n a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠ o̠da obhin b̠o̠ka̠ awa eten.  
\v 11 Ebula̠ o̠ku̠a, A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ afi̠ri̠ma ma̠ a̠limon ola̠ o̠su̠su̠ghu̠d̠i̠ i̠ru̠ru̠an d̠awa b̠o̠ka̠ awa ema̠ra̠ ma̠ igunugha̠ bho̠.  
\v 12 Sa̠ ta̠ a̠mite ma̠ ola̠ ta̠ osobh ase̠ obhumeni ma̠ eb̠la̠ ogbo ya̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠, ya̠a̠ na̠ eba̠ra̠ kuma̠ od̠ighi i̠karabh bho̠. 
\s1 Na̠ O̠so̠n Inyin Oten 
\p  
\v 13 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, i̠yar na̠ o̠se̠bh A̠zib̠a̠ kigiel kigiel ebula̠ inyin ogbo ya̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠tula̠n bho̠. Ezin bho̠ A̠zib̠a̠ aso̠n inyin oten ka̠ o̠pu̠r ob̠eton bho̠, d̠a̠ o̠wo̠l oten a̠limon ta̠ E̠mu̠gh E̠tu̠tu̠ bho̠, wa̠ ta̠ a̠d̠ighi ma̠ ola̠ inyin ta̠ o̠b̠ab̠ala d̠a̠ ebula̠ agu̠o̠ inyin uma̠ra̠ ma̠ a̠gia̠ga̠i bho̠.  
\v 14 I̠na awo̠l d̠a̠ Ib̠eb̠i Asu̠gbagba d̠o̠yo̠ ya̠ i̠yar u̠gba unigha̠ inyin bho̠ a̠bhelegi inyin, ma̠ inyin o̠te̠i̠ a̠bin d̠inyin d̠a̠ isosorogia̠n ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st.  
\v 15 O̠ku̠a a̠d̠ighi be̠le̠ni̠, a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, i̠kpo̠ ma̠ ologi ma̠ e̠mara d̠a̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ i̠yar u̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin bho̠, ya̠ i̠d̠u̠a d̠a̠ aru̠nu̠ d̠i̠yar imite bho̠ bo̠d̠o̠ d̠a̠ ra̠lebh ya̠ i̠yar u̠ge̠ uruom inyin bho̠.  
\v 16 Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st na̠ agu̠o̠ na̠ A̠zib̠a̠ O̠we̠de̠ d̠i̠yar, wa̠ a̠tula̠n i̠yar bho̠, d̠a̠ ebula̠ igbirigbir d̠o̠yo̠ sa̠ a̠nigha̠ i̠yar alu̠kpo̠ ologi ya̠ ekunuguma̠ o̠to̠ na̠ a̠ga̠i eb̠em ologi bho̠,  
\v 17 akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ rologi na̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin d̠a̠ ob̠eb̠i ka̠ ob̠eb̠i abar ola̠ inyin na̠ ogir na̠ iya̠ inyin na̠ ofugh. 
\c 3  
\s1 Apo̠l a̠puru ma̠ osiseiny onigha̠ awa 
\p  
\v 1 D̠a̠ ipa̠n i̠di̠ar bha̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠gba na̠ onigha̠ inyin a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠ ma̠a̠, isiseinye ma̠ enigha̠ i̠yar agu̠o̠ ola̠ Ib̠eb̠i O̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ta̠ e̠sasaragi̠an onyen, na̠ a̠nwunom o̠da obhin na̠ edim, agu̠o̠ aro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 2 Isiseinye ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ A̠zib̠a̠ ta̠ a̠tenemeni i̠yar d̠a̠ aru̠gu̠o̠ id̠im na̠ id̠ighi ma̠ i̠karabh a̠nwunom, ezin bho̠ ko̠ni̠ko̠ni̠ ta̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ O̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ bho̠.  
\v 3 Ya̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ wa̠ na̠ a̠sibh ogua̠n bho̠, ta̠ akpo̠me̠ni̠ ma̠ a̠ruzu d̠inyin a̠guri inyin esi eko a̠sigimeni ma̠ O̠karabh O̠ni̠ bho̠.  
\v 4 I̠yar onwuna̠ ma̠ alu̠kpo̠ ologi d̠a̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ ma̠a̠, inyin na̠ ogir agu̠o̠ i̠yar u̠gba unigha̠ inyin bho̠, sa̠ inyin ta̠ o̠ro̠ ma̠ ogir ogir o̠ku̠a nyen.  
\v 5 Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ a̠rileghom rologi d̠inyin d̠a̠ etula̠n ta̠ A̠zib̠a̠ na̠ a̠ma̠ne wa̠ Akrai̠st na̠ a̠nigha̠ bho̠. 
\s1 A̠kikiom ya̠ igboloma̠ ma̠ e̠gbu̠o̠r 
\p  
\v 6 A̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, i̠yar na̠ obhin d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st na̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ na̠ o̠gba na̠ onigha̠ inyin ma̠a̠, isigima̠ ma̠ ogbo ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ onin ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠ ya̠ na̠ erugh ado̠l e̠gbu̠o̠r, na̠ ogbo ya̠ o̠tu̠o̠no̠m d̠o̠ ma̠ atu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ ya̠ i̠yar u̠tu̠ghu̠me̠ni̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 7 Inyin o̠mar ologhom ma̠a̠, akpe̠ inyin o̠ta ado̠l d̠i̠yar agu̠o̠ i̠yar o̠ro̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ i̠gbu̠o̠ro̠gbu̠o̠r d̠a̠ igiel bho̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠.  
\v 8 I̠yar ubhin d̠o̠ ma̠ ed̠ia̠n d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ od̠e ma̠ inwo nyen. Kpe̠le̠me̠ni̠ bha̠ i̠yar ugir ogir a̠d̠uga̠la̠n na̠ etita̠n, ogbosuom a̠ruzu, ma̠ agu̠o̠ ola̠ i̠yar ko onigha̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠ni̠ inyin a̠dol\f + \fr 3:8 \fq A̠dol \ft okoko ipa̠n aru̠nu̠\f*.  
\v 9 Bo̠d̠o̠ ma̠ ola̠ i̠yar onwuna̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ a̠dila̠de a̠limon opuru inyin o̠lo̠gh agu̠o̠ onigha̠ i̠yar, ya̠a̠ i̠yar ugir o̠ku̠a b̠o̠ka̠ inyin o̠ta ma̠ a̠ma̠rugh d̠i̠yar.  
\v 10 Odi abar eka̠, i̠yar u̠lo̠gh oloko onigha̠ inyin ma̠ igiel bho̠ i̠yar u̠ro̠ na̠ inyin bho̠ ma̠a̠, “O̠ni̠ ola̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ ogir ogir o̠te̠i̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ abar d̠a̠ agu̠o̠ opa̠n o̠ni̠ a̠d̠e. O̠ni̠ ola̠ ogir d̠o̠ od̠e d̠o̠.”  
\v 11 I̠yar na̠ o̠mu̠gho̠n ma̠a̠, idi inyin na̠ orugh ado̠l e̠gbu̠o̠r, sa̠ opa̠n abar ola̠ na̠ egir bo̠ a̠ten o̠d̠u̠a esi oten esi na̠ i̠me̠ghe̠nyan.  
\v 12 I̠yar na̠ o̠gba na̠ o̠kparame̠ni̠ na̠ onigha̠ ma̠ a̠nwunom ya̠ o̠ku̠a, sa̠ i̠yar na̠ o̠le̠gh awa d̠a̠ a̠d̠ien ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st, ma̠ o̠ro̠ d̠a̠ ekima̠, obhin aru̠gu̠o̠ d̠awa ogir o̠te̠i̠ ed̠ia̠n ya̠ awa ta̠ ed̠e.  
\v 13 Ya̠a̠ inyin a̠rumor na̠ aru̠marani̠, ogir ib̠eb̠i o̠tabh d̠o̠ inyin.  
\v 14 I̠mare̠ ma̠ ekpon elelegi ma̠ o̠ni̠ ola̠ oma̠ra̠ d̠o̠ ma̠ o̠nagha o̠nu̠o̠kpe̠ d̠i̠yar, ya̠ i̠yar u̠ge̠ d̠a̠ a̠lebh onon bho̠. O̠ni̠ ko od̠ed̠ia̠n o̠ni̠ ola̠ oku̠a, b̠o̠ka̠ i̠na a̠d̠igh ari̠ghe̠l.  
\v 15 Ku̠ku̠m eka̠, o̠ni̠ ko oguri i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ o̠ni̠ o̠lo̠gi̠an a̠d̠ien, ya̠a̠ ikikiome i̠na ma̠ agu̠o̠ umor bo̠d̠o̠ u̠marani̠ d̠a̠ onin ologi ima̠ra̠ bho̠. 
\s1 Ibheleguma̠ Ekunuguma̠ Bho̠ 
\p  
\v 16 Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ na̠ agu̠o̠, wa̠ na̠ a̠nigha̠ ma̠ ekima̠ bho̠, a̠nigha̠ inyin ekima̠ kigiel kigiel d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ re̠kal. Wa̠nwuna̠ bho̠ aro̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ inyin.  
\v 17 Ami̠ Apo̠l na̠ agu̠o̠, ibhin agu̠o̠ d̠ami̠ age̠ ma̠ ibheleguma̠ ya̠ od̠i d̠a̠ a̠lebh onon bho̠. Ami̠ na̠ age̠ ma̠ o̠ku̠a ma̠ o̠ro̠ elegh d̠a̠ eb̠la̠ ra̠lebh d̠ami̠.  
\v 18 E̠no̠gho̠man ta̠ Wa̠nwuna̠ i̠yar A̠zizo̠s Akrai̠st e̠ro̠ na̠ eb̠la̠ inyin.